	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				so you resort to name calling? LOL wow. Your true nature comes out.<BR>
<BR>
I've never denided that good drops come from dragons BUT for me or other Wizards to complete certain quests you need good dragon OR giant faction (and you can't have both)! Why is this so hard to understand? Maybe because your not a wizard and therefore have no clue as to what I'm talking about? I think so. you pick your faction and deal with it and/or spend many hours fixing it.<BR>
<BR>
To be arrogant (as you stated) I'd have to say that Wizards are the best class over all the others which, is not true (even tho Micheal Jordan in now a Wizard) and I never did. To say I think Wizards are by far better travelers? well, it got you all upset didnt I? it's my opinion and I feel I've justified and presented some very soild points to make that claim without name calling. Every class is the best at something. Why are you so offended by that? whats the real issue you have here?<BR>
<BR>
IMHO wizards are more than DD dealers and taxi's. We can snare/root, debuff, stun, reduce fire/cold resists (SoTF), evac, instant argo to save a party members life, and much more. I think I even pointed out Wizard weaknesses a few posts back.<BR>
<BR>
So don't come to the Wizard board and tell me I'm arrogant because I find positives about my class. Don't come hear and knock Wizards because you have some unresolved, pentup anger and decide to flame. you dont see me on other boards flaming because some other class did something to me. I said what I said to present positives about the class and I'll stand behind them. If that offends you then dont read. simple.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
